<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="resetting-preferences-to-default-settings" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Resetting Preferences to Factory Default Settings</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p>You can reset all the <xref href="specifying-preferences.xml">settings specified in the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword></xref> to the default settings.<note>
          <p>This will also remove the user-customized GUI layout settings saved at <filepath>c:\Documents and Settings\<varname>&lt;YOUR_LOGIN&gt;</varname>\.serna-<varname>&lt;VERSION&gt;</varname>\*.sui</filepath>,  but will not affect GUI layout customization made at  the Template Original Level. For more information about Serna view files and Serna view levels, see <xref href="views.xml"/>.</p>
        </note></p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Close all documents.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the <keyword>General tab</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>General tab.</title>
            <image href="preferences-dialog-general-tab-reset-to-factory-settings.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Reset to Factory Settings</uicontrol> button.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>In the <uicontrol>Reset to Factory Settings Dialog</uicontrol>, click the <uicontrol>Proceed</uicontrol> button.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>Reset to Factory Setting Dialog.</title>
            <image href="reset-to-factory-settings-dialog.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
        <stepresult>
          <p>Serna will reset settings and shut down.</p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
